a.n: World Grand Prix Fight TNA, 1/4th finals, TATNEFT CUP, Tatneft Arena, Kazan, Russia

p.d: The first part of the quarter-finals of the "TATNEFT CUP" tournament, which took place in Kazan (Russia), at the "Tatneft Arena" in Ice Sports Palace. Six events are scheduled for the event in three weight categories involving fighters from all over the world.
